=Required software=
:* [http://www.microsoft.com/express/download/default.aspx Microsoft® Visual C++ 2008 Express Editions] ''(current: Final)''
:* [http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyId=3671e40c-d700-4509-9ed0-30e00ea38a9C Microsoft® Platform SDK] ''(current: 1/2/2008 "for Windows Server 2008 Release Candidate 0 and .NET Framework 3.5 Beta2")''
:* [http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=529f03be-1339-48c4-bd5a-8506e5acf571 Microsoft® DirectX SDK - August 2007 or earlier] ''(needed for DirectMusic, more later)''
:* [http://www.microsoft.com/downloads/details.aspx?FamilyID=4b78a58a-e672-4b83-a28e-72b5e93bd60a Microsoft® DirectX SDK - November 2007 or later] ''(current: November 2007)''


